com.oss.teamwork.teamshare.group
Class Session

java.lang.Object
  com.oss.teamwork.teamshare.group.Session

public class Session
extends java.lang.Object

Represents the account of the logged-in Teamshare user. Other users have access/create the User object of that user, not the Account. The Account stores more information than an User object, such as the number of groups the user is member of, which is not visible to other users.

Field Summary
protected  Device device
          The Device object for this account, on which the current user is logged in.
protected  Mailbox mailbox
          A reference to the user's mailbox, a repository that stores and provides access to the logged-in user's messages.
protected  java.util.Collection<Group> myGroups
          The groups the user is member of.
protected  java.util.Collection<Group> ownedGroups
          The groups the user is owner of (it is a subset of mygroups).
